Application architecture will determine how effectice your app is and how effective it is when handling requests(querys, redirects etc).

What if you get many requests and demands on the app?

-OPTION 1_(Infrastructure as a service)
	Run the apps code on mamy computers. 
	Decouple the app.(Share Nothing Architecture)

-Option 2_(Platform as a service)
	There are many providers (Engine yard, Red Hat OpenShift,
	Google App Engine, Appfog, Windows Azure)
		Each is different and vary on cost and 
		languages used. 
